                            <comment id="16869633" author="gtully" created="Fri, 21 Jun 2019 16:01:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Not sure why MemoryUsage must override the wait, wait(timeout) wait high water mark etc from Usage. I was tempted to delegate (ie delete the impls in memory usage) but there must be some good reason for the specialisation.&lt;br/&gt;
I have used the same pattern as usage.wait(..) with the MAX_VALUE to signal for ever. It is not ideal but consistent and does fix the root cause.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
